      "court_date": "2010-04-20 9:00 AM",
      "matters": "Petition For Order Confirming Trust Assets<br>Off Calendar Apr-20-2010 Granted Per Written Order<br>MINI MINUTES: Appearances: Cynthia Lee for Florence Chang.<br><br>The Court stated that the Filbert Street and Jackson Street properties in San Franciso, the San Bruno property, the Truckee property, the Palo Alto property and the Cotati property were confirmed assets of the Trust but that the Las Vegas property, the Honolulu property and the Bank of America accounts were not. The Court granted the petition as to the above assets (subject to the written order).<br><br>Judge: Mary E. Wiss. Reporter: Robert Balian, CSR#5520. Clerk: Rosie Noguera. Bailiff: Deputy B. Bloom.<br>",
